    "title": "Entry-Level Business Development Manager at Lodha Group",
    "description": "Lodha Group has an exciting opening for a Business Development Manager at our Rajkot office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Lodha Group:\nLodha Group is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage relationships with existing customers post-purchase\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n• Liaise with banks and NBFCs for home loan assistance to customers\n• Provide advisory services on property investment and market trends\n• Conduct market research and provide competitive analysis\n• Manage RERA documentation and compliance requirements\n• Prepare presentations and proposals for institutional clients\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in MS Office\n• Proficiency in Contract Management\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Negotiation Skills\n• Proficiency in Property Valuation\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n• Proficiency in Portfolio Management\n• Proficiency in RERA Compliance\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Learning & development budget\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Rajkot, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Lodha Group!",
